  <entry>
    <id>https://www.thunderbird.net/en-US/thunderbird/149.0/releasenotes/</id>
    <title type="html">Thunderbird 149.0</title>
    <author>
      <name>Thunderbird</name>
      <uri>https://www.thunderbird.net</uri>
    </author>
    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.thunderbird.net/en-US/thunderbird/149.0/releasenotes/"/>
    <updated>2026-03-24T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <published>2026-03-24T00:00:00+00:00</published>

    <content type="html"><![CDATA[
      

  
  

  
    

    
      
        
        

        
          <h3>What’s New</h3>
        

        
        
          <ul>
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Enable exporting selected address book cards</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Starred EWS messages now persist across devices</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        
          </ul>
        

        
          <h3>Changed</h3>
        

        
        
          <ul>
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Address books are now created in Account Hub</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        
          </ul>
        

        
          <h3>Fixed</h3>
        

        
        
          <ul>
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Shift-click for 'Edit' button in drafts header view did not work</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>"Replace All" in Compose did not update plain text until dialog closed</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>"Repair text encoding" could duplicate recipient and attachments</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Link colors were difficult to read in dark themes</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Pressing Delete on Trash folder could remove it without confirmation</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Renaming of a 'unified folder' created a duplicate</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Folder tree "new messages" star no longer displayed</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Reason for revoked certificate was not shown</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>"Open and show" for OpenPGP signed message could fail if headers after content-type</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Encrypted Gmail CSE emails with outer opaque S/MIME were not readable</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>"Generate and save a CSR file as... " no longer worked for S/MIME</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Cancelled attachment reminder in compose did not return focus to message body</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Thunderbird could crash while importing mail thread</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Unlabeled column visibility toggle button was not announced by screen readers</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Could not save message to external file from EWS account</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>"After Sending" filters were not working correctly</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Thunderbird did not report refused POP3 connection</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>EWS messages could fail to sync in some scenarios</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Remove message body retention policy was not functional</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Publish Calendar only showed empty OK/Cancel popup and did not publish</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Dismissed Gmail calendar reminder did nothing and item stayed visible</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Could not export local calendar as HTML</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Cancelled filter edit dialog closed the message filter dialog</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Visual and UX improvements</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p><a href="https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/security/known-vulnerabilities/thunderbird/#thunderbird149">Security fixes</a></p>
          
        </li>
      
    
    </ul>
  
  

<p>As always, you’re encouraged to <a href="https://connect.mozilla.org/t5/ideas/idb-p/ideas/label-name/thunderbird">tell us what you think</a>, <a href="https://support.mozilla.org/questions/new/thunderbird">ask for help</a>, or <a href="https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/enter_bug.cgi?product=Thunderbird">file a bug in Bugzilla</a></p>
<style> li p { display: inline; } </style>
      ]]>
    </content>
  </entry>
  
  <entry>
